      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Description of the Collection</head>
         <p>Erotic pulp fiction related to male cross-dressing, forced feminization, and other transgender activity.</p>
         <p>Publisher for some later titles: Tri-Cite/Star Distributors.</p>
         <p>Titles for issues 101-116 (see accompanying list) taken from cover.</p>
         <p>All titles paperbound.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
